---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'May 2026';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — Sanchi Enterprises"
  description="Privacy policy for Sanchi Enterprises. How we collect, use, and protect information submitted through our exhibition carpet enquiry forms."
  breadcrumbs={[{ name: 'Privacy Policy', item: 'https://www.sanchienterprises.com/privacy-policy' }]}
>
  <Navbar />
  <main>

    <section class="legal-hero" aria-labelledby="privacy-heading">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="legal-hero__inner">
          <span class="eyebrow eyebrow--inverse eyebrow--line" data-animate>Legal</span>
          <h1 class="legal-hero__title" id="privacy-heading" data-animate data-delay="1">
            Privacy Policy
          </h1>
          <p class="legal-hero__meta" data-animate data-delay="2">
            Sanchi Enterprises &nbsp;·&nbsp; Last updated {lastUpdated}
          </p>
          <p class="legal-hero__intro" data-animate data-delay="3">
            This policy explains what information we collect when you use this website
            and how we handle it. We collect only what is necessary to respond to your enquiries.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="legal-body">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="legal-content">

          <section class="legal-section" aria-labelledby="pp-s1">
            <h2 class="legal-section__title" id="pp-s1">1. Who We Are</h2>
            <p>
              Sanchi Enterprises is an exhibition carpet supply and installation business
              operating across India, with offices in New Delhi and Mumbai. We are the data
              controller for personal information collected through this website.
            </p>
            <p>
              Contact:&nbsp;
              <a href="mailto:kanav@sanchienterprises.com">kanav@sanchienterprises.com</a>
              &nbsp;·&nbsp;
              <a href="tel:+919958132189">+91 99581 32189</a>
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="legal-section" aria-labelledby="pp-s2">
            <h2 class="legal-section__title" id="pp-s2">2. Information We Collect</h2>
            <p>
              We collect information only when you voluntarily submit our contact form. The form
              requests:
            </p>
            <ul>
              <li>Full name</li>
              <li>Company or organisation name</li>
              <li>Phone number</li>
              <li>Email address</li>
              <li>Event or show name</li>
              <li>Event location</li>
              <li>Requirement details (carpet type, area, dates, installation needs)</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
              We do not operate user accounts, require registration, or store payment information.
              Browsing this website anonymously requires no personal data.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="legal-section" aria-labelledby="pp-s3">
            <h2 class="legal-section__title" id="pp-s3">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <p>The information you submit is used solely to:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Respond to your exhibition flooring enquiry</li>
              <li>Prepare and send a product or pricing proposal</li>
              <li>Coordinate supply and installation logistics for your event</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
              We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal information to any third party.
              We do not use it for unsolicited marketing without your consent.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="legal-section" aria-labelledby="pp-s4">
            <h2 class="legal-section__title" id="pp-s4">4. How Your Enquiry Is Transmitted</h2>
            <p>
              When you submit the contact form, your information is formatted as a WhatsApp
              message and sent directly to our team via WhatsApp (wa.me). The transmission
              occurs through your device's WhatsApp application. We do not store form submissions
              in a database on our servers.
            </p>
            <p>
              WhatsApp is operated by Meta Platforms Ireland Limited. Their privacy practices
              govern messages sent and received through their service.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="legal-section" aria-labelledby="pp-s5">
            <h2 class="legal-section__title" id="pp-s5">5. Third-Party Services</h2>
            <p>This website uses the following third-party services:</p>

            <h3 class="legal-section__subtitle">Cloudflare Turnstile</h3>
            <p>
              We use Cloudflare Turnstile to protect the contact form from automated spam
              submissions. Turnstile analyses browser signals to verify that a submission
              originates from a human. Cloudflare may process technical data such as your
              IP address and browser attributes as part of this verification. No Turnstile
              tokens or challenge data are stored by us after the verification completes.
              Cloudflare's privacy policy applies: <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">cloudflare.com/privacypolicy</a>.
            </p>

            <h3 class="legal-section__subtitle">Google Fonts</h3>
            <p>
              This website loads typefaces (DM Sans, Inter, Cormorant Garamond) from Google
              Fonts CDN. When your browser requests a font file, Google may log your IP address
              and the referring URL. Google's privacy policy applies: <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">policies.google.com/privacy</a>.
            </p>

            <h3 class="legal-section__subtitle">Vercel (hosting)</h3>
            <p>
              This website is hosted on Vercel. Vercel may retain standard web server access
              logs (IP address, timestamp, requested URL, HTTP status) for infrastructure and
              security purposes. Vercel's privacy policy applies: <a href="https://vercel.com/legal/privacy-policy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">vercel.com/legal/privacy-policy</a>.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="legal-section" aria-labelledby="pp-s6">
            <h2 class="legal-section__title" id="pp-s6">6. Cookies</h2>
            <p>
              This website does not set first-party cookies. Third-party services (Cloudflare
              Turnstile, Google Fonts) may set cookies or use browser storage as part of their
              normal operation. These are governed by those services' own policies.
            </p>
            <p>
              We do not use tracking cookies, advertising pixels, or analytics cookies.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="legal-section" aria-labelledby="pp-s7">
            <h2 class="legal-section__title" id="pp-s7">7. Data Retention</h2>
            <p>
              Because enquiry data is transmitted via WhatsApp and not stored in a server-side
              database, retention is governed by our internal WhatsApp business communication
              practices. We retain enquiry correspondence only for as long as is necessary to
              fulfil the business purpose for which it was shared.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="legal-section" aria-labelledby="pp-s8">
            <h2 class="legal-section__title" id="pp-s8">8. Your Rights</h2>
            <p>
              Under the Digital Personal Data Protection Act 2023 (India) and applicable
              privacy laws, you have the right to:
            </p>
            <ul>
              <li>Request access to personal data we hold about you</li>
              <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
              <li>Request erasure of your data where we have no legitimate ongoing purpose to retain it</li>
              <li>Withdraw consent to processing at any time</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
              To exercise any of these rights, contact us at&nbsp;
              <a href="mailto:kanav@sanchienterprises.com">kanav@sanchienterprises.com</a>.
              We will respond within 30 days.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="legal-section" aria-labelledby="pp-s9">
            <h2 class="legal-section__title" id="pp-s9">9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
            <p>
              We may update this policy when our practices change or when legal obligations
              require it. The "Last updated" date at the top of this page reflects the most
              recent revision. Continued use of this website after an update constitutes
              acceptance of the revised policy.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="legal-section" aria-labelledby="pp-s10">
            <h2 class="legal-section__title" id="pp-s10">10. Contact</h2>
            <p>
              For any privacy-related enquiries or data requests, contact us at:<br />
              <strong>Sanchi Enterprises</strong><br />
              Email: <a href="mailto:kanav@sanchienterprises.com">kanav@sanchienterprises.com</a><br />
              Phone: <a href="tel:+919958132189">+91 99581 32189</a>
            </p>
          </section>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-hero {
    background-color: var(--color-navy-dark);
    padding: var(--sp-8) 0 var(--sp-7);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .legal-hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 70% at 80% 50%, rgba(27,42,107,0.30) 0%, transparent 62%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .legal-hero__inner {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 720px;
  }
  .legal-hero__title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(34px, 4.5vw, 56px);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.08;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    color: var(--color-text-inverse);
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-2);
  }
  .legal-hero__meta {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(247,246,243,0.40);
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-3);
  }
  .legal-hero__intro {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.72;
    color: rgba(247,246,243,0.64);
    max-width: 560px;
  }

  .legal-body {
    background-color: var(--color-warm-white);
    padding: var(--sp-7) 0 var(--sp-8);
  }
  .legal-content {
    max-width: 720px;
  }

  .legal-section {
    padding-bottom: var(--sp-6);
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-6);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);
  }
  .legal-section:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }
  .legal-section__title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    color: var(--color-navy-dark);
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-3);
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  .legal-section__subtitle {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin-top: var(--sp-4);
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-2);
  }
  .legal-section p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.82;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    opacity: 0.82;
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-3);
  }
  .legal-section p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .legal-section ul,
  .legal-section ol {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.82;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    opacity: 0.82;
    padding-left: var(--sp-4);
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-3);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
  }
  .legal-section a {
    color: var(--color-navy);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }
  .legal-section a:hover { color: var(--color-navy-dark); }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .legal-hero { padding: var(--sp-7) 0 var(--sp-6); }
    .legal-section__title { font-size: 18px; }
  }
</style>
